result.name: Malacca Cusine

reviews.text:
***Three stars all go to food only.***
Ticket queuing system was smooth, however service wasn’t meeting basic expectations.

Ordered curry chicken rice and unfortunately waited for 25 mins. Obviously kitchen was out of capacity and focused on external orders via deliveroo etc. Staff were not 

I believe it’s something to be addressed - if the volume cannot be handled, perhaps try to add premium to control the demand a bit and avoid missing orders for walk-in customers.

Furthermore the “ultra-a/c” is pretty extreme to make the hot food getting cold within few minutes, I would assume it’s one of the tactics to expedite the cycling of customers. 
i.e. asking people to get the meal done and leave
Good value for money. Their beef rendang is so good. I'll definitely come back.
Food is ok, but the cold drinks are room temperature...

Laksa soup was rich in taste. Fish ball and noodle were good. Bak Kut Teh soup was mild but the pork meat was too tough and chewy. The toast in kaya tasted very good with a thick cut salty butter. Very nice!
Low cost with nice food

result.name: 馬六 - 海南雞.喇沙.肉骨茶

reviews.text: 普通價錢，普通味道: 今日食咗新加坡喇沙滲滲，唔難食但又唔算得好食，得椰汁同辣味，無咩香料香葉的層次感，兩隻蝦又實又無味。 下次想試個蝶豆花飯 (聽朋友講話唔錯)，喇沙就應該唔會再食啦!!  馬拉拉茶幾好飲的!!

西灣河馬六可以話係最近食過最好嘅海南雞飯！
今次食晏嚟試，叫咗海南雞飯，馬拉棧通菜。
海南雞真的做到皮香肉滑，油飯亦值得一讚，雞油香味十足，真材實料！
就個人口味而言，如果雞肉可以肥少少重好！一定更加美味更加滑。

喇沙湯底夠味
係魚蛋唔太夠彈牙（唔知係咪因為新加坡魚蛋係無咁彈）
落單同招呼嘅員工都幾有禮貌

馬六

夠大份有雞味的雞
乾硬恰到好處的飯
味道各有特色的醬
刺激暖身入味的湯

合理價錢，可以一戰
食物還可以，但餐廳內有難聞的氣味🤢
